snippet.title: The creation of 'Korean fire noodle' BULDAK
snippet.description:
#buldak #firenoodles #mukbang 

Rolled-out flour passes through hot steam tunnels.
When noodles are steamed and passed through a mold, they transform into square shapes. 
The noodles are immediately fried in palm oil for 60 seconds to make them crispy. 
They are cooled quickly and packed with ramen seasoning powder, and then Buldak Ramen was created to cross the sea. 
Samyang Food's Miryang factory produces 800 packets of ramen per minute for export. 

[Park In-soo / Head of Miryang Factory: Compared to other factories, the mixer is the most automated part. We're spinning three lines, and two people do it automatically. It's a process that can be controlled via mobile devices, reducing the number of people by more than 50%.]

Samyang Food invested 240 billion won in building the Miryang Factory. 
Exports increased rapidly, prompting the construction of a new factory.
Miryang is located adjacent to Busan Port, which allows for reduced logistics costs.
Samyang Food aims to generate 1 trillion won in sales for the first time this year.

[Han Se-hyuk / Head of Samyang Food Global Support Division: In the 1st quarter, not only China, but also the United States, Southeast Asia and 
the European market has also experienced significant expansion. The proportion of overseas sales is about 60-70%. So, maybe we can continue to grow even more than that…]

In 2022, the Buldak brand's overseas sales amounted to 480 billion won, which has been increased by 6,400 times from its launch in 2012. 
With the Miryang Factory now fully operational, Samyang Food's overseas expansion is expected to accelerate.

snippet.description:
새우와 튀김의 느끼함을
극강의 매콤함으로 꽉잡아불닭🔥

🧡두 번째 속닭임 : 불닭말이 깐쇼새우 레시피🧡

1) 먼저 새우를 깨끗하게 씻어 물기를 제거한다.
2) 새우는 머리를 떼어내고 껍질과 내장을 제거한다.
3) 손질한 새우에 소금과 후추를 뿌려 밑간을 해준다.
4) 새우에 간이 배는 동안 불닭볶음면의 면을 익힌다.
5) 다음으로 소스를 준비한다. 물 반 컵, 불닭볶음면 액상스프, 케첩 3 큰 술, 설탕 4 큰 술, 식초 1/2 큰 술, 소금 약간을 넣고 잘 섞는다.
6) 밑간이 된 새우에 전분가루를 묻힌 후 불닭볶음면의 면을 돌돌 감아준다.
7) 팬에 기름을 넉넉하게 붓고 가열한다. 기름의 온도가 올라가면 새우의 모양이 흐트러지지 않도록 잘 튀겨준다. 새우가 노릇해지면 건져낸다.
8) 팬에 고추기름 3 큰 술, 다진 파, 다진 마늘, 다진 생강을 넣고 볶는다. 여기에 미리 만들어준 소스를 넣고 끓여준다. 소스는 감자 전분으로 묽기를 조절한다.
9) 이제 소스에 불닭말이 새우튀김을 넣고 버무려준다
10) 양상추를 올린 접시에 불닭말이 깐쇼새우를 예쁘게 담아준다. 취향에 따라 파슬리 가루, 삶은 완두콩, 땅콩 가루 등을 뿌린다.
